@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.cos(((v1 + 0.67 * v0 + 0.82) - 0.18))
    v2 = (wp.abs((v2 + 0.15 - tmp + 0.10)) - tmp)
    tmp = (wp.abs((v2 + 0.70 * v2 + 0.81)) - (wp.cos(v2 + 0.52) + (v0 + 0.24 + v2 + 0.69)))
    v1 = ((v1 + (v0 + 0.17 - v0 + 0.87)) / 0.64)
    v0 = wp.exp(0.12)
    data[tid] = v0
